About this app

Do you want to use dual account on one Phone? If you want to separate your personal account & business account then use Clone App for whatsapp multi accounts parallel app. Clone App for whatsapp latest is a free app to run multiple accounts for whatsapp, receive messages and chat with friends and family with different account on one device by QR code scan through your What'scan which makes chat messenger easy to use with only one click. Clone App dual account or super clone app copy an account on any device and can use 2 accounts for whatsapp on one Device. This application is a helper to download a communication service app in order for you to stay connected with your family and friends that helps you to multichat or get the most special features that only are available on the GB-Clone App for whatsapp latest version to amaze your friends with some hidden extension. Clone App- App Cloner & dual app helps clone and run multiple accounts for whatsapp online simultaneously on one phone to separate work and life. It is very stable, small in size and much faster app and also free and very simple to use.
How to clone App dual Account, and is it an effective method? You can easily clone your personal account for whatsapp to another phone by scanning the QR Code. With "Multiple Accounts & App Cloner for WhatsApp", you can not only use multiple accounts for whatsapp but also synchronize all your account information such as conversations, photos, videos, audio and document files very quickly. You can also download Status and direct message.
